# amifldrv64.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 


### Description

amifldrv64.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 34fa6ba4-dc7c-4fd6-b947-8a0bb8ebd031
- **Created**: 2023-01-09
- **Author**: Michael Haag, Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**: [] | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/khulnasoft-labs-io/mitigate-drivers/raw/main/drivers/0dff47f3b14fb1c1bad47cc517f0581a.bin" "Download" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create amifldrv64.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\amifldrv64.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start amifldrv64.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
